      <title>尼日利亚意外加息半个百分点以抑制通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-25/nigeria-surprises-with-half-point-hike-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚中央银行将借贷成本提高至历史新高，以抑制通货膨胀、支持奈拉并吸引投资，此举令金融市场感到意外。彭博新闻社的 Ondiro Oganga 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-25/nigeria-surprises-with-half-point-hike-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:28:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
